#### **背景 (Background) 对照表**

**示例：**

```naninovel
@back 23_6 Scale:{g_backgroundDefaultScale} !Lazy
; 最上面的黑色遮罩层VerticalBlindGradually特效消失
@back Transparent.Custom SubId:"Overlay" dissolve:"VerticalBlindGradually" tint:"#000000" time:0.99 !Lazy
; 等待一小会到特效演完
@Wait "0.9"
``` 

